            "title": "深圳跟進放寬購房限制 以期提振樓市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 深圳跟進中國其他大城市放寬購房規定，這是中國當局應對長期房地產危機所做的最新努力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">深圳市住房和建設局及中國央行深圳市分行周五晚間發布公告，符合商品住房購買條件的該市戶籍居民家庭，以及自購房之日前在深圳連續繳納社會保險或個人所得稅滿1年及以上的非該市戶籍居民家庭，在羅湖區、寶安區（不含新安街道）、龍崗區、龍華區、坪山區、光明區範圍內購買商品住房不限套數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府還表示，各銀行業金融機構在利率定價機制安排方面不再區分首套住房和二套住房。新規自9月6日起施行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前北京和上海分別於8月推出放寬住房限購的政策。與此同時，中國百強房企8月銷售繼續下滑，房價下跌以及兩大一線城市加碼樓市刺激未能提振需求。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UzfwC1P8yHDHjHy.8bm5KQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b4f0319cc8c9c2d92296ddf6b6e7d836\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Shenzhen Joins Major Cities in Easing Home-Buying Rules</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Foster Wong、Li Liu、Jacob Gu.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
