            "title": "數碼港企業融資累計逾462億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"數碼港企業融資累計逾462億\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TuKb7_ay6DbWREz2ykRPeQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/7f1db560-8ac1-11f0-bfe7-4114cb14b48a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">數碼港企業融資累計逾462億</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
